Description: #django-coupons
        
        ![build status](https://travis-ci.org/byteweaver/django-coupons.png)
        
        A reuseable Django application for coupon gereration and handling
        
        
        ##Contributors
        (alphabetical order)
        
        @akuryou
        @ikresoft
        @noxan
